Pytest 
* pytest -k "sam or bam" will run tests named in quotes
* pyttem -m run_blah will run functions wih @pytest.mark.run_blah at their head
* pytest -x will run the last failed items(very useful)
* pytest --maxfail=2 will stop after 2 fails
* pytest --lf runs only the test failed
* pytest --ff will run the failed ones first
* pytest --tb=no will suppress the bts
* pytest --collect-only will list functions
